measurement.rubric:
You are a senior portfolio manager evaluating the quality of a stock buy thesis generated by an AI system. Score each criterion below and return ONLY valid JSON.
You will receive: the stock's signal data, the generated thesis, and the risk assessment.
{ "signal_convergence": float 0.0-1.0, // how many signals genuinely agree? are they independent? "thesis_quality": float 0.0-1.0, // specific and actionable vs generic boilerplate? "risk_assessment": float 0.0-1.0, // is the invalidation condition concrete and testable? "alert_precision": float 0.0-1.0, // based on prior performance data if available, else 0.5 "composite": float 0.0-1.0, // weighted average "concerns": [], // any red flags in the analysis "recommendation": "alert" | "watch" | "skip" }

stage.user:
Analyze {ticker} ({company_name}) for a potential buy opportunity.
Today: {date}. Current price: ${current_price}.

=== TECHNICAL SIGNALS ===
RSI(14): {rsi_14}
MACD: {macd_signal}
Price vs SMA20/50/200: {sma_distances}
Bollinger position: {bollinger_position}
52w high/low distance: {distance_from_52w_high_pct}% / {distance_from_52w_low_pct}%
Volume ratio (today/20d avg): {volume_ratio}x

=== FUNDAMENTAL SIGNALS ===
P/E: {pe_ratio} | Forward P/E: {forward_pe} | PEG: {peg_ratio}
Revenue growth YoY: {revenue_growth_yoy}%
Earnings growth YoY: {earnings_growth_yoy}%
FCF margin: {free_cash_flow_margin}%
Gross margin trend: {gross_margin_trend}
Debt/Equity: {debt_to_equity}

=== SENTIMENT SIGNALS ===
Recent news: {news_sentiment}
Prior earnings sentiment: {earnings_context}

=== CATALYST SIGNALS ===
Options flow (last 48h): {options_flow}

=== MACRO CONTEXT ===
{macro_context}

Score each signal category as bullish/neutral/bearish with a confidence,
then compute an overall signal count. Return JSON:
{{
  "signals": {{
    "technical":   {{"direction": "bullish"|"neutral"|"bearish", "confidence": float, "key_factor": string}},
    "fundamental": {{"direction": "bullish"|"neutral"|"bearish", "confidence": float, "key_factor": string}},
    "sentiment":   {{"direction": "bullish"|"neutral"|"bearish", "confidence": float, "key_factor": string}},
    "catalyst":    {{"direction": "bullish"|"neutral"|"bearish", "confidence": float, "key_factor": string}},
    "macro":       {{"direction": "bullish"|"neutral"|"bearish", "confidence": float, "key_factor": string}}
  }},
  "bullish_count": int,      // 0-5
  "weighted_score": float,   // weighted by signal_weights in parameters
  "proceed_to_thesis": true | false  // true if bullish_count >= 3
}}

Write a buy thesis for {ticker} at ${current_price}.

Signal summary: {signal_scoring.signals}
Weighted score: {signal_scoring.weighted_score}
Prior opportunities alerted: {prior_opportunities}

Return JSON:
{{
  "entry_price_range": "{lower}-{upper}",
  "primary_trigger": string,        // the single most important reason to buy NOW
  "supporting_factors": [list of 2-3 strings — the other bullish signals],
  "target_price_30d": float,
  "target_price_90d": float,
  "expected_return_pct": float,
  "timeframe": "days" | "weeks" | "months",
  "conviction": "high" | "medium" | "low",
  "thesis_summary": string max 120 words — specific, no boilerplate
}}

Stress-test this buy thesis for {ticker}:
{thesis_generation.thesis_summary}

Entry: {thesis_generation.entry_price_range}
Target 30d: ${thesis_generation.target_price_30d}

Current fundamentals: PE={pe_ratio}, revenue_growth={revenue_growth_yoy}%
Macro context: {macro_context}

Return JSON:
{{
  "stop_loss_price": float,                  // specific price level
  "invalidation_condition": string,           // the one thing that kills the thesis
  "primary_risk": string,                     // biggest threat
  "secondary_risks": [list of 2 strings],
  "risk_reward_ratio": float,                 // (target-entry) / (entry-stop)
  "max_position_size_suggestion": "small" | "medium" | "normal",
  "hold_through_earnings": true | false,
  "risk_summary": string max 80 words
}}

alerts.format:
📈 BUY SIGNAL: {ticker} @ ${current_price}
🎯 Target: ${thesis_generation.target_price_30d} (30d) | Stop: ${risk_assessment.stop_loss_price}
⚖️ R/R: {risk_assessment.risk_reward_ratio}x | Conviction: {thesis_generation.conviction}
🔥 Trigger: {thesis_generation.primary_trigger}
⚠️ Risk: {risk_assessment.invalidation_condition}
📊 Signals: {signal_scoring.bullish_count}/5 bullish | Score: {signal_scoring.weighted_score}
